post_text:
Reminder: All Denville PK-8 Schools will be closed from March 16-March 27, 2020. We will revisit the closure during the week of March 23, 2020 in consultation with our school physician, Department of Health and our team.

March 16, 2020 will be used as one of our four remaining snow closing days. This will give the staff some additional preparation time for the Flexible Instruction Days, which will start on March 17, 2020.

This website has a great deal of information related to the COVID-19 and Flexible Instruction Days. http://www.denville.org/district/c_o_v_i_d-19_and_extended_closure

The district will publicize a Frequently Asked Questions Document on March 16, 2020.

If you have any questions or comments please contact me at sforte@devnille.org.
